query.sql: select cr.*, 'catalog_page' || CP_CATALOG_PAGE_ID as local_id, cr_returned_date_sk as report_date from TPCDS_SF10TCL.catalog_returns cr left join TPCDS_SF10TCL.catalog_page cp on cr_catalog_page_sk = cp_catalog_page_sk

SELECT c_customer_sk, ca_state, cd.*, 1 as ro, 1 as ro2, 1 as ro3 FROM TPCDS_SF10TCL.customer c JOIN TPCDS_SF10TCL.customer_demographics cd on c_current_cdemo_sk = cd.cd_demo_sk JOIN TPCDS_SF10TCL.customer_address ca on c.c_current_addr_sk = ca.ca_address_sk

select HD_DEMO_SK, HD_VEHICLE_COUNT, HD_BUY_POTENTIAL, HD_DEP_COUNT, concat(cast(IB_LOWER_BOUND as string), ' - ', cast (IB_UPPER_BOUND as string)) as income_band from TPCDS_SF10TCL.INCOME_BAND, TPCDS_SF10TCL.HOUSEHOLD_DEMOGRAPHICS where IB_INCOME_BAND_SK = HD_INCOME_BAND_SK
select distinct ss_customer_sk, d_date_sk from TPCDS_SF10TCL.store_sales, TPCDS_SF10TCL.date_dim where ss_sold_date_sk = d_date_sk

SELECT sr.*, 'store channel' as sales_channel, 'store' || s_store_id as local_id, sr_returned_date_sk as report_date FROM TPCDS_SF10TCL.store_returns sr LEFT JOIN TPCDS_SF10TCL.store s on sr_store_sk = s_store_sk

column.name: Morning Time Tier
column.sql: CASE WHEN "T_HOUR" = 8 AND "T_MINUTE" >= 30 THEN '08:30 to 09:00' WHEN "T_HOUR" = 9 AND "T_MINUTE" < 30 THEN '09:00 to 09:30' WHEN "T_HOUR" = 9 AND "T_MINUTE" >= 30 THEN '09:30 to 10:00' WHEN "T_HOUR" = 10 AND "T_MINUTE" < 30 THEN '10:00 to 10:30' WHEN "T_HOUR" = 10 AND "T_MINUTE" >= 30 THEN '10:30 to 11:00' WHEN "T_HOUR" = 11 AND "T_MINUTE" < 30 THEN '11:00 to 11:30' WHEN "T_HOUR" = 11 AND "T_MINUTE" >= 30 THEN '11:30 to 12:00' WHEN "T_HOUR" = 12 AND "T_MINUTE" < 30 THEN '12:00 to 12:30' ELSE 'Other' END

query.sql: select wr.*, ws.ws_web_site_sk as wsr_web_site_sk, s.web_site_id, 'web_site' || s.web_site_id as local_id, wr_returned_date_sk as report_date from TPCDS_SF10TCL.web_returns wr left outer join TPCDS_SF10TCL.web_sales ws on ( wr.wr_item_sk = ws.ws_item_sk and wr.wr_order_number = ws.ws_order_number) left join TPCDS_SF10TCL.web_site s on ws_web_site_sk = web_site_sk

select cs.*, 'catalog_page' || CP_CATALOG_PAGE_ID as local_id, cs_sold_date_sk as report_date, wh.w_warehouse_sq_ft from TPCDS_SF10TCL.catalog_sales cs left join TPCDS_SF10TCL.catalog_page cp on cs_catalog_page_sk = cp_catalog_page_sk left join TPCDS_SF10TCL.warehouse wh on cs_warehouse_sk = w_warehouse_sk

column.name: Catalog Sales Price Tier
column.sql: CASE WHEN "CS_SALES_PRICE" BETWEEN 0 AND 500 THEN '500 or Less' ELSE 'More than 500' END

query.sql: select distinct cs_ship_customer_sk as customer_sk, cs_sold_date_sk as sold_date_sk from TPCDS_SF10TCL.catalog_sales UNION ALL select distinct ws_bill_customer_sk as customer_sk, ws_sold_date_sk as sold_date_sk from TPCDS_SF10TCL.web_sales ws

SELECT ca.ca_state, cd.* FROM TPCDS_SF10TCL.customer c, TPCDS_SF10TCL.customer_address ca, TPCDS_SF10TCL.customer_demographics cd WHERE c.c_current_addr_sk = ca.ca_address_sk and c.c_current_cdemo_sk = cd.cd_demo_sk

SELECT customer_sk, sold_year, CASE WHEN total_catalog > total_non_catalog THEN true ELSE false END catalog_preferred FROM ( SELECT customer_sk, sold_year, SUM( CASE WHEN sale_type IN ('c') THEN year_total ELSE 0 END) total_catalog, SUM( CASE WHEN sale_type IN ('s', 'w') THEN year_total ELSE 0 END) total_non_catalog FROM ( SELECT ss_customer_sk customer_sk, d_year sold_year, 's' sale_type, SUM(((ss_ext_list_price-ss_ext_wholesale_cost-ss_ext_discount_amt)+ ss_ext_sales_price)/2) year_total FROM TPCDS_SF10TCL.store_sales, TPCDS_SF10TCL.date_dim WHERE ss_sold_date_sk = d_date_sk GROUP BY 1, 2, 3 UNION ALL SELECT ws_bill_customer_sk customer_sk, d_year sold_year, 'w' sale_type, SUM(((ws_ext_list_price-ws_ext_wholesale_cost-ws_ext_discount_amt)+ ws_ext_sales_price)/2) year_total FROM TPCDS_SF10TCL.web_sales, TPCDS_SF10TCL.date_dim WHERE ws_sold_date_sk = d_date_sk GROUP BY 1, 2, 3 UNION ALL SELECT cs_bill_customer_sk customer_sk, d_year sold_year, 'c' sale_type, SUM(((cs_ext_list_price-cs_ext_wholesale_cost-cs_ext_discount_amt)+ cs_ext_sales_price)/2) year_total FROM TPCDS_SF10TCL.catalog_sales, TPCDS_SF10TCL.date_dim WHERE cs_sold_date_sk = d_date_sk GROUP BY 1, 2, 3 ) t GROUP BY 1,2) z
SELECT p.*, ss.* FROM TPCDS_SF10TCL.promotion p INNER JOIN TPCDS_SF10TCL.store_sales ss ON ss.ss_promo_sk = p.p_promo_sk

SELECT ss.*, sr.*, case when (sr_returned_date_sk - ss_sold_date_sk <= 30) then '<= 30 days' when (sr_returned_date_sk - ss_sold_date_sk > 30) and (sr_returned_date_sk - ss_sold_date_sk <= 60) then '31-60 days' when (sr_returned_date_sk - ss_sold_date_sk > 60) and (sr_returned_date_sk - ss_sold_date_sk <= 90) then '61-90 days' when (sr_returned_date_sk - ss_sold_date_sk > 90) and (sr_returned_date_sk - ss_sold_date_sk <= 120) then '91-120 days' else '> 120 days' end as returns_time_tier, 1 as returns_count, 'store channel' as sales_channel, 'store' || s_store_id as local_id, sr_returned_date_sk as report_date FROM TPCDS_SF10TCL.store_returns sr INNER JOIN TPCDS_SF10TCL.store_sales ss ON ss.ss_ticket_number = sr.sr_ticket_number AND ss.ss_item_sk = sr.sr_item_sk AND ss.ss_customer_sk = sr.sr_customer_sk LEFT JOIN TPCDS_SF10TCL.store s on sr_store_sk = s_store_sk
select ss.*, 'store' || s_store_id as local_id, ss_sold_date_sk as report_date from TPCDS_SF10TCL.store_sales ss left join TPCDS_SF10TCL.store cp on ss_store_sk = s_store_sk

column.name: Sales Price Tier
column.sql: CASE WHEN "SS_SALES_PRICE" > 200 THEN '200 and More' WHEN "SS_SALES_PRICE"BETWEEN 150 AND 200 THEN '150-200' WHEN "SS_SALES_PRICE" BETWEEN 100 AND 150 THEN '100-150' WHEN "SS_SALES_PRICE" BETWEEN 50 AND 100 THEN ' 50-100' ELSE ' 50 and Less' END

column.name: Net Profit Tier
column.sql: CASE WHEN "SS_NET_PROFIT" > 25000 THEN 'More than 25000' WHEN "SS_NET_PROFIT" BETWEEN 3000 AND 25000 THEN '3000-25000' WHEN "SS_NET_PROFIT" BETWEEN 2000 AND 3000 THEN '2000-3000' WHEN "SS_NET_PROFIT" BETWEEN 300 AND 2000 THEN '300-2000' WHEN "SS_NET_PROFIT" BETWEEN 250 AND 300 THEN '250-300' WHEN "SS_NET_PROFIT" BETWEEN 200 AND 250 THEN '200-250' WHEN "SS_NET_PROFIT" BETWEEN 150 AND 200 THEN '150-200' WHEN "SS_NET_PROFIT" BETWEEN 100 AND 150 THEN '100-150' WHEN "SS_NET_PROFIT" BETWEEN 50 AND 100 THEN ' 50-100' WHEN "SS_NET_PROFIT" BETWEEN 0 AND 50 THEN ' 0- 50' ELSE ' 50 or Less' END

query.sql: select distinct ss_customer_sk, ss_customer_sk as bridge_customer_sk, ss_sold_date_sk from TPCDS_SF10TCL.store_sales

select ws.*, ws.ws_web_site_sk as wsr_web_site_sk, s.web_site_id, 'web_site' || s.web_site_id as local_id, ws_sold_date_sk as report_date, wh.w_warehouse_sq_ft from TPCDS_SF10TCL.web_sales ws left join TPCDS_SF10TCL.web_site s on ws_web_site_sk = web_site_sk left join TPCDS_SF10TCL.warehouse wh on ws_warehouse_sk = w_warehouse_sk

calculated-member.name: Web Catalog Sales Price Growth
calculated-member.expression: [Measures].[m_ws_cs_ext_sales_price_sum] / (ParallelPeriod([Sold Date Dimension].[Sold Date Week Hierarchy].[Sold Calendar Week], -53, [Sold Date Dimension].[Sold Date Week Hierarchy].CurrentMember), [Measures].[m_ws_cs_ext_sales_price_sum])

calculated-member.expression: [Measures].[Store and Web Purchased Amount] / (ParallelPeriod([Sold Date Dimension].[Sold Date Week Hierarchy].[Sold Calendar Year-Week], 1, [Sold Date Dimension].[Sold Date Week Hierarchy].CurrentMember), [Measures].[Store and Web Purchased Amount])

calculated-member.name: Catalog Purchased Amount Growth
calculated-member.expression: [Measures].[m_purchased_amount_in_catalog] / (ParallelPeriod([Sold Date Dimension].[Sold Date Week Hierarchy].[Sold Calendar Year-Week], 1, [Sold Date Dimension].[Sold Date Week Hierarchy].CurrentMember), [Measures].[m_purchased_amount_in_catalog])

calculated-member.name: Avg Quarterly Store Sales for 1998-1999
calculated-member.expression: Avg( [Sold Date Dimension].[Sold Date Dimension].[Sold Calendar Quarter].&[1998-02-01]:[Sold Date Dimension].[Sold Date Dimension].[Sold Calendar Quarter].&[1999-02-01], [Measures].[m_store_sales_price])

calculated-member.name: Avg Quarter Sales Ratio
calculated-member.expression: CASE WHEN ([Measures].[m_store_sales_price] - [Measures].[Avg Quarterly Store Sales for 1998-1999]) < 0 THEN -1 * ([Measures].[m_store_sales_price] - [Measures].[Avg Quarterly Store Sales for 1998-1999]) ELSE ([Measures].[m_store_sales_price] - [Measures].[Avg Quarterly Store Sales for 1998-1999]) END /[Measures].[Avg Quarterly Store Sales for 1998-1999]

calculated-member.name: Catalog and Web Sales per Warehouse SqFt

properties.caption: Catalog and Web Sales per Warehouse SqFt

calculated-member.expression: IIF( [Measures].[Warehouse Size - Web] > 0, [Measures].[Catalog and Web Sales] / [Measures].[Warehouse Size - Web], [Measures].[Catalog and Web Sales] / [Measures].[Warehouse Size - Catalog] )

calculated-member.name: Web Sales Increase
calculated-member.expression: CASE WHEN ISEMPTY([Measures].[m_ws_ext_sales_price_sum]) THEN NULL ELSE ([Sold Date Dimension].[Sold Date Dimension].CurrentMember, [Measures].[m_ws_ext_sales_price_sum]) / ([Sold Date Dimension].[Sold Date Dimension].CurrentMember.PrevMember, [Measures].[m_ws_ext_sales_price_sum]) END

calculated-member.name: Store Sales Increase
calculated-member.expression: CASE WHEN ISEMPTY([Measures].[m_ss_ext_sales_price_sum]) THEN NULL ELSE ([Sold Date Dimension].[Sold Date Dimension].CurrentMember, [Measures].[m_ss_ext_sales_price_sum]) / ([Sold Date Dimension].[Sold Date Dimension].CurrentMember.PrevMember, [Measures].[m_ss_ext_sales_price_sum]) END
